                        <h4>Course Outline</h4>
                        <p>Most importantly, you will be able to express yourself in the most common situations and also discuss more specialized topics.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>المعجزة الخالدة - The eternal miracle</li>
                            <li>يوم في حياة ناشئ - A day in a junior's life</li>
                            <li>أقلياتنا في العالم - Our minorities around the world</li>
                            <li>السنة النبوية - Prophetic Sunnah</li>
                            <li>الأطفال والقراءة - Children and reading</li>
